{"tid":36911,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傅振中成功握手送卡 力撐CY好特首：永遠愛您","createTime":"2016-12-13T04:38:20.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T05:28:06.000Z","uid":48093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b86970e924a765df2abd93bdd8a9e38e1366a8f4","tid":36911,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:38:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161213/large/1481597306_91c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161213%2Flarge%2F1481597306_91c8.jpg&h=242595a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161213/large/1481597308_2599.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161213%2Flarge%2F1481597308_2599.jpg&h=dfdf7559&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161213/large/1481597311_7395.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161213%2Flarge%2F1481597311_7395.jpg&h=eea3578d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161213/large/1481597314_3d0a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161213%2Flarge%2F1481597314_3d0a.jpg&h=6552414a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「珍惜群組」和「保衛香港運動」共20多人，今早在梁振英宣佈不連任特首後首次行會前，在特首辦門外拉起「感謝特首過去辛勞和貢獻永遠愛您」橫額，又舉起「CY我撐你」、「疾風知勁草，板蕩識忠臣」等標語，準備到行會示威區見梁振英，不少人戴上太陽眼鏡。「收工男」傅振中更率先入場，佔據示威區有利位置。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英其後現身特首辦示威區，20多名保衛香港和珍惜群組成員即高喊「梁振英！好特首！」、「好感激你呀，特首！」口號，梁振英則在對方高喊口號近一分鐘後，才舉手示意對方停止，聆聽其他示威者訴求。<br />\n<br />\n20多名保衛香港和珍惜群組成員其後再次高喊口號，引起其他示威者不滿，高喊:「你地停一停得唔得呀？」，梁振英即再示意有關人士停喊口號。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英接著與多名保衛香港運動成員握手，包括「收工男」傅振中，傅振中則說「支持你」，並試圖送上已開打、寫有成員簽名的紀念卡，但梁振英未有接過，其後回頭時才接收傅振中已「摺埋」的紀念卡。<br />\n<br />\n傅振中其後即與成員離開特首辦，並叫成員「唔使再戴頂藍帽嘞」。"},{"pid":"7f07da5c6469e0b4c44df755eae1702d22e528ce","tid":36911,"uid":22080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:39:34.000Z","msg":"屌呢班垃圾真係好嘔心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"944a72904d8fe82eba51bb8e24061452e4be6902","tid":36911,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:40:04.000Z","msg":"傅振中其後即與成員離開特首辦，並叫成員「唔使再戴頂藍帽嘞」。<br />\n<br />\n收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcdfd6e2f5e73539850cae1627ac6f689f433663","tid":36911,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:40:07.000Z","msg":"其實呢啲幾錢一次？"},{"pid":"11bc4440a4e86f30b05b755c8812427454c16102","tid":36911,"uid":491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:41:50.000Z","msg":"又振中又振英<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0b87ce029cd5b78dbe17814f3702f933ba779d8","tid":36911,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:43:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"706d5b72b244a5bfd88de65b59431894a2de49bd","tid":36911,"uid":50790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:47:38.000Z","msg":"嘩，好撚噁心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46ca6a9d563e8f5dae5fcd6522c35c5accee9f6a","tid":36911,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:47:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cb666228fcbc4c43fefb86fb4e1b6120ccf30e30","tid":36911,"uid":35919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:51:30.000Z","msg":"唔講以為689就死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a85d51bc294c21b54e4cf804ba5c127048f075fa","tid":36911,"uid":7008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:56:27.000Z","msg":"又有得加人工"},{"pid":"cb457381a430c05bb5e73248ac4017bd9f036396","tid":36911,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0